# elephant providers required by this setup.
#
# elephant (walker's data backend) loads compiled Go plugins (.so) from
# ~/.config/elephant/providers/. Those binaries are build artifacts - platform
# specific and regenerable - so they are NOT tracked in this repo.
#
# This file is just the manifest of which providers to build/install on a new
# machine. elephant itself ignores it (it only scans providers/*.so); it exists
# for you and the dotfiles workflow.
#
# On a fresh machine: install elephant, build/install the providers below, then
# verify with:  ls ~/.config/elephant/providers/
#
# One provider per line:
calc
clipboard
desktopapplications
files
providerlist
runner
symbols
websearch
